com.tapsterrock.mpx
Class MPXUnits

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.tapsterrock.mpx.MPXUnits
public class MPXUnits
extends java.lang.Object

This class deals with an odd case where the max units value, which is a percentage, is represented as a float between 0 and 1. The formatting used by MSP is not the same as that used for all other floats, hence this special case.
